OL,3,CCommons committee chairman says local
OL,4,Croads are 'riddled with potholes'
OL,6,FThe cost of bringing pothole-plagued
OL,7,Flocal roads in England and Wales up to
OL,8,Fscratch has been estimated at #16.3
OL,9,Fbillion.
OL,11,FThe PAC's report stated that the DfT
OL,12,F"has not set out what outcomes it
OL,13,Fexpects" from its funding for local
OL,14,Froads maintenance, nor "sought to
OL,15,Fevaluate its impact".
OL,17,FIt added: "The department has overall
OL,18,Fpolicy responsibility for local roads
OL,19,Fbut has shown too little interest in
OL,20,Fwhat difference its funding of local
OL,21,Froads maintenance has made."
