OL,6,FLocal roads maintenance funding for
OL,7,FEngland provided by the Government in
OL,8,Fthe 2025/26 financial year will be
OL,9,Fnearly #1.6 billion, representing a
OL,10,F#500 million uplift compared with the
OL,11,Fprevious 12 months.
OL,13,FThe PAC also found that the DfT "does
OL,14,Fnot have a good grasp of the condition
OL,15,Fthat local roads in England are really
OL,16,Fin".
OL,18,FIt stated there are "too many gaps in
OL,19,Fthe data it collects".
