OL,6,FThe DfT's data suggests local road
OL,7,Fconditions have been "broadly stable"
OL,8,Fbut this "does not reflect what
OL,9,Fpeople, businesses and local
OL,10,Fauthorities are experiencing," the PAC
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FSir Geoffrey said: "The declining
OL,14,Fstate of England's local roads is a
OL,15,Fnational embarrassment.
OL,17,F"As well as harming the prospects for
OL,18,Four economy and communities' own
OL,19,Fsocial wellbeing, highways riddled
OL,20,Fwith potholes pose an increasing
OL,21,Fsafety threat to road users.
