OL,3,CCommons committee chairman says local
OL,4,Croads are 'riddled with potholes'
OL,6,F"Alarmingly, however, not only is the
OL,7,Fstate of our local roads on the
OL,8,Fdownslope, our inquiry shows
OL,9,FGovernment are having to find out
OL,10,Fabout these issues from industry
OL,11,Fbodies and road users themselves due
OL,12,Fto their own patchy data.
OL,14,F"This committee has long raised
OL,15,Fconcerns around a failure across
OL,16,FGovernment departments to effectively
OL,17,Ffund and plan for the future, a theme
OL,18,Fthat is certainly on show here, along
OL,19,Fwith an overly tangled web of
OL,20,Faccountability."
