OL,6,FThe PAC recommended that the DfT
OL,7,Fclearly set out "roles and
OL,8,Fresponsibilities" for itself and local
OL,9,Fauthorities in ensuring local roads
OL,10,Fare "maintained to a good standard
OL,11,Fthroughout England".
OL,13,FIt also called on the department to
OL,14,F"simplify" its funding for local roads
OL,15,Fand "provide more long-term certainty".
