OL,6,FA DfT spokesperson said: "For far too
OL,7,Flong our roads have been left to
OL,8,Fcrumble, and this PAC report has laid
OL,9,Fbare the result of the decades of
OL,10,Fdecline we have inherited in our road
OL,11,Finfrastructure.
OL,13,F"That's why we're investing a record
OL,14,F#1.6 billion for the coming year to
OL,15,Fhelp local authorities fix up to seven
OL,16,Fmillion more potholes.
