OL,3,CCommons committee chairman says local
OL,4,Croads are 'riddled with potholes'
OL,6,FAdam Hug, transport spokesman for the
OL,7,FLocal Government Association, said:
OL,8,F"Greater long-term funding certainty
OL,9,Ffor local highways authorities ` with
OL,10,Ffive-yearly funding allocations on a
OL,11,Fpar with National Highways ` is needed
OL,12,Fto tackle the multibillion-pound local
OL,13,Froads backlog, as this report
OL,14,Frecommends."
OL,16,FIt emerged on Wednesday that the total
OL,17,Fcost of repairing vehicles damaged by
OL,18,Fpotholes hit a record high last year.
